- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automata and language transformation algorithms.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper introduces new theoretical concepts for finding state complexities.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper discusses state complexity.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) may be relevant as the paper deals with automata and their functions.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) may be relevant as the paper discusses the representation of functions by letters.
